data.description: Move-in ready home with an OVERSIZED LOT and open layout concept. This home is located inside a gated community with community pool, playground, elementary school direct access and a nice walking trail.  Home has an open kitchen concept with breakfast bar and granite countertops to host and overseeing different rooms of the home plus a whole home water system. Additionally to the Master Bedroom, another bedroom has its very own bathroom. It has tile through out  common areas and carpet in all bedrooms with a full size walk-in shower in the master bathroom. The laundry room with washer & dryer is conveniently located by garage door for easy drop off of dirty shoes and items. Community is located within proximity to all theme parks, just minutes to shopping, hospitals, Osceola Sheriff Department HQ and restaurants. It is Near St Cloud Lakefront Park, Remington Golf Course, and Orlando International Airport, as well as easy access to FL turnpike and major highways. Seller is providing $5,000 towards buyers closing cost with full price offer!
